Experimental fast-init implementation for ARCHLINUX

Edit your /boot/grub/menu.lst
add init=/sbin/finit-arc to your kernel line
Example: kernel /boot/vmlinuz26-eee root=/dev/sda2 ro init=/sbin/finit-arc quiet

!!! WARNING !!!
Finit doesn't support UUIDs. Then you must replace UUIDs
with /dev/sdx devices in /boot/grub/menu.lst and /etc/fstab.

If you want autostart X edit /etc/finittab


